author: @GoldenFairy97
text:
dear Jeon JungKook, 
  how are you today? Please sleep enough hours, and always take care of yourself, just as you take care of ARMY. You are a very special light in our lives and I want to thank you for keeping me smiling and feeling happy every single day. 
  I want to tell you that you always, always, ALWAYS inspire me to be happy and to do what brings me happiness, what brings me comfort, what I love to do. You have a very special meaning to me and I don't know if you ever read a comment from me or a letter, I wish that I could know - maybe tell me via telepathy? heheâ™¥ï¸Â - but I want to thank you for saving my days, my nights, for healing my heart every time it gets broken. You motivate me to keep going, you motivate me to do even things that may seem to be simple but that once were hard for me. You motivate me to stay healthy, to keep eating what I enjoy eating, to dance, to follow what brings me happiness. You know, I love photography so much just as you, so I love to photograph the sky, the stars, the moon, clouds. My dream it's to see a butterfly and being able to take a photo, but I think they are very shy hehe .. did you ever took a photo of a butterfly?  I would love to see. You have so much talent, I am sure that you can catch a very beautiful one. My favorite ones are the Monarch ones. Actually my name's Vanessa and Vanessa means Butterfly, and that makes me feel proud of my name. . and I once heard that, whenever we see a butterfly, we should close our eyes and make a wish, they carry our wishes and it may comes true. So do that okay JK â™¥ï¸ make a wish in case you see a butterfly, i am sure they will make your dream come true. You deserve only the best in your life, you really do and you deserve to be reminded that you are somebody very talented, hardworking who motivates, and inspires all of us. You are so amazing. 

please keep those words inside your heart, and if you ever read this letter, i hope a butterfly lets me know, and that my wish can come true. . 

I hope you are happy today, and everyday of your life. You deserve to be happy, you deserve to shine, you deserve the best in your life. Thank you for existing.

Hello Jungkook, I hope that you can read this letter or maybe you can feel those words by telepathy. Firstly, I wish that you can wake up happy and smiling, I wish you a wonderful day and that you do something that brings you love and happiness. . Today wasnt really easy for me but you always bring me happiness, and make me feel better. You may read this a lot and i hope that you know how special you are in this world, you are like a fairy healer to us. You heal us just by being who you are, you bring us happiness by smiling and being as happy as you can be. You are somebody really special in this world, Jungkook. 
  I wish that I could thank your parents, because you exist and your existence really makes everything better and brighter in this world. I bet the stars above the sky are so proud of you, because they know somebody here in earth is shining and bringing light to so many people around. You are a very precious light and i will always be here to see you shining and doing your best everyday. I am so grateful to live in a world with you exist. Thank you for fixing my heart and bringing me comfort and peace. 

even in my bad days, you know how to make me smile and making me feel better. I hope this letter can make you feel loved and special, you are really loved in this world. 
I purple you, I love you so so much. and please never forget that, you are saving people lives, thank you for being so important in my life. always shine, okay?
